---
title: Chinese Cashew Turkey Stir-Fry  with Garlic Rice
description: Packed with plenty of veggies and tender turkey, this dish is a perfect recipe to make for a weeknight meal! Made with authentic Chinese flavours, a touch of spice and served over garlic rice, this dish is a perfect alternative to your favourite take out!
